@startuml FR-16-Melihat_Guide_Penggunaan_Website

title Sequence Diagram: FR-16 Melihat Guide Penggunaan Website

' ============================================
' DAFTAR AKTOR DAN OBJEK (LIFELINE)
' ============================================
' Aktor:
'   - User: Pengguna yang melihat guide
' Objek:
'   - GuidePage: Halaman panduan (Boundary)
'   - StepCard: Kartu langkah panduan (Boundary)
'   - GuideController: Controller panduan
'   - CheckAvailabilityPage: Halaman ketersediaan (Boundary)
'   - MyReservationsPage: Halaman reservasi (Boundary)

actor "User" as User

boundary "GuidePage" as GuidePage
boundary "StepCard" as StepCard
control "GuideController" as GuideCtrl
boundary "CheckAvailabilityPage" as AvailPage
boundary "MyReservationsPage" as MyRes

' ============================================
' SKENARIO 1: MELIHAT HALAMAN GUIDE
' ============================================
== Melihat Halaman Guide ==

User -> GuidePage: Akses halaman "Guide"
activate GuidePage

GuidePage -> GuideCtrl: getGuideContent()
activate GuideCtrl

GuideCtrl --> GuidePage: guideSteps[]
deactivate GuideCtrl

loop untuk setiap langkah (1-6)
    GuidePage -> StepCard: render(stepData)
    activate StepCard
    StepCard --> GuidePage: cardComponent
    deactivate StepCard
end

GuidePage --> User: Tampilkan panduan:\n1. Cek Ketersediaan\n2. Reservasi Online\n3. Smart Approval\n4. Ketentuan Waktu\n5. E-Permit\n6. Layanan 24/7

deactivate GuidePage

' ============================================
' SKENARIO 2: MEMBACA STEP CEK KETERSEDIAAN
' ============================================
== Membaca Step Cek Ketersediaan ==

User -> StepCard: Membaca Step 1: Cek Ketersediaan
activate StepCard

StepCard --> User: Tampilkan informasi:\n- Icon kalender\n- Judul: "Cek Ketersediaan"\n- Deskripsi langkah-langkah\n  mengecek jadwal fasilitas

deactivate StepCard

' ============================================
' SKENARIO 3: NAVIGASI KE CEK KETERSEDIAAN
' ============================================
== Navigasi ke Halaman Ketersediaan ==

User -> GuidePage: Klik tombol "Cek Ketersediaan"
activate GuidePage

GuidePage -> AvailPage: navigate("/availability")
activate AvailPage

AvailPage --> User: Tampilkan halaman Check Availability

deactivate AvailPage
deactivate GuidePage

' ============================================
' SKENARIO 4: MEMBACA STEP RESERVASI ONLINE
' ============================================
== Membaca Step Reservasi Online ==

User -> GuidePage: Kembali ke halaman Guide
activate GuidePage

User -> StepCard: Membaca Step 2: Reservasi Online
activate StepCard

StepCard --> User: Tampilkan informasi:\n- Icon form\n- Judul: "Reservasi Online"\n- Deskripsi cara mengisi\n  formulir pemesanan digital

deactivate StepCard
deactivate GuidePage

' ============================================
' SKENARIO 5: MEMBACA STEP SMART APPROVAL
' ============================================
== Membaca Step Smart Approval ==

User -> StepCard: Membaca Step 3: Smart Approval
activate StepCard

StepCard --> User: Tampilkan informasi:\n- Icon checklist\n- Judul: "Smart Approval"\n- Deskripsi proses persetujuan\n  oleh admin

deactivate StepCard

' ============================================
' SKENARIO 6: NAVIGASI KE RIWAYAT RESERVASI
' ============================================
== Navigasi ke Riwayat Reservasi ==

User -> GuidePage: Klik tombol "Riwayat Reservasi"
activate GuidePage

GuidePage -> MyRes: navigate("/my-reservations")
activate MyRes

MyRes --> User: Tampilkan halaman My Reservations

deactivate MyRes
deactivate GuidePage

@enduml
